      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Zest your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Cut the <strong>lemon[s] </strong>into 4 wedges per lemon</p>",
