      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 450ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[675ml]</span> [900ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and stir in your <strong>soft cheese </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
